# Web UI — React SPA

## Stack
Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS v4 + shadcn/ui + Lucide icons. No class-variance-authority patterns — use plain Tailwind. Build: `cd frontend && pnpm run build`.

## Design System (Linear-inspired dark theme)
- Background: zinc-950 base, zinc-900 sidebar/panels
- Accent: indigo-500 (sidebar, agent badges, active states)
- Status icons: circle (pending), spinner (in_progress), check (completed), x (cancelled)
- Priority: colored bar indicators — red (urgent), orange (high), yellow (medium), grey (low)
- Flat sections, no heavy card borders. Mobile-first responsive.

## Component Patterns

### Wrapper components must forward props to the inner component
When a component destructures props (e.g. `{ children }`) and renders a third-party component inside, explicitly pass those props through. A self-closing tag like `<ReactMarkdown ... />` silently renders nothing — it must be `<ReactMarkdown ...>{children}</ReactMarkdown>`. TypeScript won't catch this because `children` is a valid prop on the outer function; it just never reaches the inner component.

### Use Lucide icons, not emoji or Unicode symbols
All iconography must use Lucide React components (`import { Play, Check, ... } from "lucide-react"`). Never use emoji (🔄, ✅) or Unicode symbols (▶, ✓, ⏱) in JSX — they render inconsistently across platforms and don't respect the design system's sizing/color tokens.

## Debugging Blank UI Sections
When content is missing from the UI, verify the API returns the expected data **before** investigating the frontend. Use the Python shell to call `task_store` methods directly — if the data is correct there, the bug is in the component or its children, not the backend.

## File Roles
- `Layout.tsx` — App shell: sidebar (desktop) + tab bar (mobile), FAB
- `TaskList.tsx` — Task list with status icons, priority bars, tags, time ago
- `TaskDetail.tsx` — Flat detail view: inline metadata, subtasks, markdown sections, comment avatars (indigo `Bot` icon for agent, letter avatar for users), reply-pending polling every 3s
- `TaskCreate.tsx` — Create form: priority selector, plan-only toggle, target repo datalist
- `ActivityLog.tsx` — Pipeline event log with Lucide icon map (`EVENT_ICON_MAP`), mobile-responsive
- `Login.tsx` — Minimal sign-in form
- `Markdown.tsx` — Shared renderer (`react-markdown` + `remark-gfm` + `remark-breaks`), dark-theme prose styles. `remark-breaks` converts single newlines to `<br>` so agent output line breaks are preserved. If you add a new remark/rehype plugin, install it via `npm install <pkg>` — missing packages cause `tsc` to fail with TS2307.
- `api.ts` — Fetch client with `credentials: "include"`, auto-reloads on 401
- `types.ts` — TypeScript interfaces: `Task`, `TaskDetail`, `Counts`, etc.
